{"type": "article", "id": 11658, "title": "蔺草编织篮子", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-06T11:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135608gBsGQqROaov3Xxcw.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套由台湾工匠温雪云制作的蔺草编织篮子，这项手艺是台湾传统的手艺，目前随着市场竞争的激烈，小工作坊的手艺正在失传，而台湾蔺草学会一直致力于保护传统手艺。日前，芬兰设计师卢家恩台湾蔺草学会联手推出了这一套“蔺草编织系列”作品，图案全部来自台湾地方特色，并设计了铜环抛光或是加入盖子，让篮子实用性更强。<a href=\"http://www.gaa.fi/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135742efJPRlt54rj0HLvm.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"372\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45476773\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135742RLVmfhnwrU3YudEq.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135743Pz5nakcmSjZwNFsV.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"461\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56356968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135743pnYa0s4qBit1bezX.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"614\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135744Na9ezV7itwR0shvU.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"611\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74694377\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}